**Structure Plan:** Build the post like a pre-appointment checklist — before you book, at the consultation, during the appointment, when shape goes wrong. Move the reader from anxiety to total clarity on what to say, step by step. Each H2 answers a real question the reader has in their head as they approach the appointment.

