6. **What Reference Photos to Save Before Your Appointment** *(how to pick and use inspo photos effectively — Pinterest, TikTok, the narrow almond TikTok example)*
7. **The Questions to Ask Your Nail Tech Before They Start** *(active consultation skills — length, shape type, suitability for nail bed)*
